Shatoto make big mistake
coming to Gula...

rows.label: tlk42300021_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Shatoto come from Avaritia
to do business in Gula.

rows.label: tlk42300021_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But selling goods in this city
only earn tiny profits!

rows.label: tlk42300021_01_msg0004
rows.name:
At times like this, Shatoto remember
what Mom say lots...

rows.label: tlk42300021_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Products of Shatoto not attractive
to Gula and Superbia peoples
here in Torigo.

rows.label: tlk42300021_01_msg0008
rows.name:
But Shatoto not have money to go
back to Avaritia... Oh dear!
